549
00:49:45,620 --> 00:49:49,850
Astaga. Dasimu selalu bengkok.

550
00:49:49,850 --> 00:49:51,620
Kau seperti Jun Hyun.

551
00:49:52,150 --> 00:49:54,090
Apel tidak pernah jatuh jauh
