597
00:51:56,781 --> 00:51:57,981
"Jeongseokka"./
"Jeongseokka".

598
00:51:57,981 --> 00:51:59,421
Itu dia. Jeongseokka.

599
00:51:59,580 --> 00:52:02,221
Aku yakin kalian juga putus...

600
00:52:02,221 --> 00:52:03,550
