00:52:31,681 --> 00:52:32,820
"Pengaturan"?

615
00:52:33,451 --> 00:52:34,820
Tapi kau punya nama.

616
00:52:35,890 --> 00:52:37,850
Saatnya makan siang.
Kita harus bergegas hari ini.

617
00:52:37,850 --> 00:52:39,261
Saat mereka menyajikan cumi kering goreng,...

